# pipenv
#   According to pypa/pipenv#598, it is recommended to include Pipfile.lock in version control.
#   However, in case of collaboration, if you want to share the lock file:
#Pipfile.lock

# poetry
#   Similar to Pipfile.lock, poetry.lock is of version control control.
